subject: Golf
Masters Golf Tournament
lead_paragraph: The litany of golfers shooting sub-par rounds included Justin Rose and Trevor Immelman, tied for the lead, and Zach Johnson, the defending champion. Tiger Woods, at even par, tied for 19th.
